    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2209820/extras/554a3984fe059e7f9f669fa186c2394b.avif?t=1700469157\" width=600 height=424 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2209820/extras/f3946c2737190d0ef5c7759fd4e5f653.webp?t=1700469157\" width=600 height=60 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2209820/extras/d6cd506c4c18eebc6feddb0c462a9292.poster.avif?t=1700469157\" width=600 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2209820/extras/d6cd506c4c18eebc6feddb0c462a9292.webm?t=1700469157\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2209820/extras/d6cd506c4c18eebc6feddb0c462a9292.mp4?t=1700469157\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>掌控埃尔德隆之地，并通过使用独特的守护者、法术和物品成为最伟大的召唤师，还有大量的策略待你发现！袭击其他玩家的基地，消灭他们的守卫者，摧毁他们的建筑并占领他们的能量核心以获得守护者点数和资源。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2209820/extras/39c1b554b264ebc43233c4bd853e0b0c.webp?t=1700469157\" width=600 height=60 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2209820/extras/c568efcfa73bba15e3b1fd0cc4287f85.poster.avif?t=1700469157\" width=600 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2209820/extras/c568efcfa73bba15e3b1fd0cc4287f85.webm?t=1700469157\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2209820/extras/c568efcfa73bba15e3b1fd0cc4287f85.mp4?t=1700469157\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>召集强大的守护者们，他们可以保卫你的基地，并将是与你一起冲锋陷阵的忠实战士。通过结合守护者属性、主动技能和被动特性来粉碎你的敌人！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2209820/extras/7684c9fdae39492ba695731bfb7d59e9.webp?t=1700469157\" width=600 height=60 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2209820/extras/7cf47f677e7dc73eb1d0fe8d461fd25a.poster.avif?t=1700469157\" width=600 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2209820/extras/7cf47f677e7dc73eb1d0fe8d461fd25a.webm?t=1700469157\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2209820/extras/7cf47f677e7dc73eb1d0fe8d461fd25a.mp4?t=1700469157\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>在不同国度中进行独特的单人任务，来升级你的守护者，收集资源，占据更多的能量核心。还可以到达大熔炉、神器商人和启蒙神殿等特殊地点以获得更多的力量！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2209820/extras/6548797aac28740bfb17273e2aecfdfd.webp?t=1700469157\" width=600 height=60 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2209820/extras/fdada8f763781fe6bd16b1a0001a91ba.poster.avif?t=1700469157\" width=600 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2209820/extras/fdada8f763781fe6bd16b1a0001a91ba.webm?t=1700469157\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2209820/extras/fdada8f763781fe6bd16b1a0001a91ba.mp4?t=1700469157\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>成为大型社区的一员，获得更强大的物品！你可以与你公会的伙伴交易法术和物品，并找到你缺失的锻造配方。我为人人！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2209820/extras/13528071cd7efe1ce9f8b4e3b13776d4.webp?t=1700469157\" width=600 height=60 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2209820/extras/2a9a0e507fcbc3300c825237f6eb74bd.poster.avif?t=1700469157\" width=600 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2209820/extras/2a9a0e507fcbc3300c825237f6eb74bd.webm?t=1700469157\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2209820/extras/2a9a0e507fcbc3300c825237f6eb74bd.mp4?t=1700469157\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>用你的守护者、守卫塔、陷阱和侦察兵保护你的主堡和你的能量核心。利用资源将你的基地发展成令人印象深刻的堡垒，并用各种可用的装饰品将其装饰成你的家！<br><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2209820/extras/e51bdf6762108b9b26288e021528a6a5.poster.avif?t=1700469157\" width=600 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2209820/extras/e51bdf6762108b9b26288e021528a6a5.webm?t=1700469157\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2209820/extras/e51bdf6762108b9b26288e021528a6a5.mp4?t=1700469157\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
